SystemChildren of the cr che were treated after the repairs. Photo: supplied Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories NGO ukuPhakamisa with the generous sponsorship of DCLM repaired the inside of their adopted cr che s roof recently. The roof at Nyathikazi Cr che was leaking and in addition their cupboards were damaged. According to ukuPhakamisa founder Cheryl Wolhuter the damages were affecting the children. We also purchased more tables and chairs as the creche is growing. ukuPhakamisa took the cr che under our wing about two years ago and we try our best to assist where we can. DCLM fully sponsors our projects to uplift and educate the community. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.